{
  "stem": "13469.4",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The whole old age home was taken away and deported, including our four grandparents, to Westerbork.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Can I just mention the sports again, [INAUDIBLE] [INAUDIBLE]?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was a highlight.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] And on of the few things that I do remember is that in Amsterdam, we were not allowed to play most sports, and not with other people.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Only with Jews we were allowed to play sports.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And this was for the first time when I played table tennis.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And after the war, actually, I became a bit of a table tennis star in the Midlands kind of thing.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But it started in Amsterdam, where I played table tennis for the first time.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was very strange because there was no rubber for the bats.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We played with all kind of funny concoctions.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I remember having linoleum on the batting surface for playing table tennis.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And another thing that we played there, very surprisingly, was hockey.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Hockey was always a big game in Holland.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we played mixed hockey because there weren't enough boys or girls to play individual teams.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So we played mixed hockey in those days.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So those are some of the things I remember.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Useless things for these purposes, but that's-- mine seems to have been-- I can remember car number plates from many years ago, and sports I can remember, but don't remember the important things like Judaism, I'm sorry to say.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Another thing that, perhaps, mentioning Judaism is that I should have had my bar mitzvah, actually, at the time when we were in in [INAUDIBLE], but I didn't have it.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I would imagine that there was no possibility at that time of proper synagogue services, although I may be wrong.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
